"Engine room, sick bay."
Ooh, smoothie bar!

00:17:25.670 --> 00:17:26.671
- Focus.
- Sorry.

00:17:26.755 --> 00:17:30.383
"Restroom, science lab." Oh. Escape pods!

00:17:30.467 --> 00:17:33.053
(BEEPING)

