It's the first time
I've ever been able to do this!

00:21:19.362 --> 00:21:22.073
- Buford.
- Ah, sorry. I was in the zone.

00:21:22.741 --> 00:21:24.451
Hey, we're out of the asteroid field.

00:21:24.534 --> 00:21:26.202
<i>♪ Ooh ♪</i>

00:21:29.039 --> 00:21:30.040
ISABELLA: Oh.

